\id LAM
\h Ka La
\toc1 Ka La
\toc2 Ka La
\toc3 Ka La
\mt1 LAMENTATIONS
\mt2 KA LA
\mt3 Ka La Sung Thu Umdan
\ip Jerusalem chu agalmi hoa kon manthahna achutan ahileh Lunghan, kichat, puldou chule kinepna beihil asohdoh tan ahi. Lekhabu hi Jeremiah themgaovin Jerusalem thohgimna thua aphondohna ahi. Jerusalem khopi sung thilsoh umdol, ijakai ahetsoh nunga Pathen thahat akon kinepna aum'e ti, ahil ahi.
\ip Ka La lekhabu hi abih bih in thupi akihom khen in, kinepna le manthahna, mimal lungheija kisihna, khopi chule nampi ahi. Jeremiah in lunggiltah a khopi dinga athohnatna le alung hempina ijakai A-Z bukim ahi. Lekha-gol kijih patna jouse Hebrew lekhajem hoa phatah’a akipan in ahi, ajeh chu Jeremiah in ban neicha deng chang tah’a ajih dan akilang in ahi. Hiche lekhabua kon hin Manthahna chung chang keo hilouvin, Pathen thaneina le thilbol theina jong kicheh tah in mudoh ahi.
\is1 Lekhabu Jihpa Chule Akijih Kum
\ip Ka La hi Jeremiah themgao in Jerusalem khopi chimjou 586 BC a anajih ahi.
\is1 Koi Henga Ajih Ham?
\ip Jeremiah in Nam mite manthahna’a kon alung heina diuva, ngailutna tothoa gahna anei ahi. Hahsatna dinmun’a kon nam mite lunghempina chung changa anajih ahi.
\c 1
\s1 Jerusalem Thohgimna
\p 
\v 1 Phatkhat mi ana dimsetna Jerusalem khopi chu tunvang kho gem a sodoh tai. Chitin namtin lah a ana minthang khopi chu tunvang meithai a sodoh tan ahi. Vannoi leiset lengnu dinmun ana lo chu tunvang soh dinmun alo jotai.
\v 2 Jan khovah vah'in mitlhi long chutchut in akap in ana ngailu cheng holah a jong alhamon ding aum tapouvin aloi agol chengse la aheodah leh adou gal in apang gam tauvin ahi.
\v 3 Galhingin Judah akai tauvin soh channa leh engbolna athoh tan ahi. Gam dang nammite lah a achengun kicholdona mun amujou pouvin ahi. Agalmite uvin a umkimvel’un jamdoh thei louvin akoichah tauve.
\v 4 Jerusalem lampiho akhul lhatan koimacha Pathen houna kin bol dingin ahung doh tapouvin, khopi kotpihola donlouvin aumgamtan athempu hou akhoisa gam tauvin anungah khangthah teu akhankho diu gelnan akap gam tauve.
\v 5 A sugenthei houhi a Pakaiyun apang un ajalou teuchu akhantou tul tul jengun ahi. Pakaiyin achonset jih uva Jerusalem chu aengbol uva achateu galhinga kiman a gamla tah’a kikaimang gamu ahi tauve.
\v 6 Jerusalem khopi, ahoina le aloupina chu amang thah ahitai. Alamkaiteu jong neh ding ham hing mu joulou sakhigol toh abang gam tauvin, agalmiteu masanga jam doh nading tha jong anei jou tapouve.
\v 7 Lung lengvaija Jerusalem avale laitah in, tumasanga aphatlai nikho agel doh’e. Tunla agalmite khutnoija aum tan koimacha apanhu ding aum tapoi. Agalmiteuvin ajep lhu’uvin alhu ho chu aveuvin anuisat’un ahi.
\v 8 Achonset behseh jeh'in Jerusalem ponse bangin paimangin aum tan. Tumasanga anagel thupi hon, tuhin anoisetauve, ajeh chu aponu kiho-lhah peha jumle jachat thoha um ahitaove. Hijeh chun hahdoh ngamlouhel la khoisa jing jenga um ahitai.
\v 9 Amaho hin a khonung diu kigel phah louhelin jonthanhoina in akisuhboh uve. Amaho a kemsuh jing tauvin, a lhamon diu aphong ding diu koima aum tapoi. Pakai ka hahsetnao nei vetpeh un tin akap tauve.
\v 10 Galmiten ajokhophelun anei jouseu akichom tauve. Pakaiyin a Hou-In sunga lut dia anaphallou nam dangte chun aHou-In sungu asuh boh pehu chu amudoh tauvin ahi.
\v 11 Amiteu neh ding hollin apeng jen jun tauvin, a hinjouna diuvin anei agouvu ajohdohun, vo Pakai neihin veuvin e-chan geija thet le kidah’a kaum’u hitam tin akap tauve.
\v 12 Vo chele vahle, hilang hin hopa ho hiche thilsoh hi ija na gellou u-ham? Pathen'in ka chunguva alunghan abuhlhah na le eibol gimnau hi vetem uvin.
\v 13 Aman vanna kon'in meikong ahin sep lhan kagu kachang’u ahalgo tai. Aman ka lampi uva thang a kamin eile hoitauve. Aman eichom thengselun nilhum lhumin hahsatna eithoh sahun ahi.
\v 14 Ka chonset nau khaovin eikanun sohchanna nam kolin eihenun ahi. Pakaiyin katha’u eisuh ngoi pehun kagal miteu kom'ah eipedohun akhutuva chatmon kaum taove.
\v 15 Pakaiyin kalah'uva um kami hatteu thaneina asulhan kakhang thahteu suhmangna dingin galmite amangchan ahi, Pakaiyin lengpithei chilna akisuhchip bangin akhopi hoitah chu a suchip tan ahi.
\v 16 Hiche ho jouse jeh'in kakapin kamitlhi kamaija alonglha jenjung jingin ahinlah koima eilhamon ding le eitilhembi ding aum pon ahi. Galmiten eijou khup del tauvin, kakhang thahte’u khonung ding jong abing tan ahi.
\v 17 Jerusalemin panpi ngaiyin akhut alhaang dohin ahinlah apanpi ding amu joupoi. Pakaiyin Ami Isrealte chunga, aheng akom ho chu agalmi asohdoh pehhan! Ama ho hi ponse banga paimanga um ahitai.
\v 18 Jerusalemin aseiyin Pakai hi adih’e, ajeh chu keiman ama dounan na kana tong’e, chitin namtinin ka thusei hi neingai pehun, ka thoh gimna hi neihet pehun, ka chanute’u leh ka chapa te’u khol gamla tah a galhingin eikaimang peh tauve.
\v 19 Keiman kaloi kagolte kom'a kithopina kathumin ama honla eingai peh pouve. Ka themputeu leh ka lamkaiteu khopi sung’a kelin athi gam tauve, ahinkhou kihuhdohna ding aholun amu jou pove.
\v 20 Pakai kalung lengvaina neivetpehin, ka chonset jeh'in ka lungthim ahesoh’e, kholai dung’a kitha tona aumin'insung lang’a thilong aki jam’e.
\v 21 Ka lung gim ka khoisatna mi tamtah in eijah pehin ahinlah koima chan eihung lhamon pon ahi. Ka galmiten kathoh gimna ajah phatun Pakai nangin neibolnao hi akipa piuvin ahi. Oh Pakai keiho thoh tobang banga amaho nathohsah dinga naseipihnao nikho chu lhunsah loiyin.
\v 22 Pakai ka chonset nau jeh a nei engbol bangu chun ama hon eibolsetnao hi venlang amaho jong engbolin. Ka lengvainao hi atamvalin ka lungthim sung’u asuna lheh jeng’e.
\c 2
\s1 Jerusalem Chunga Pathen Lunghana
\p 
\v 1 Pakai alunghan jal'in Jerusalem khopi hoitah chu muthim lhangkhalin atome. Isreal khopi hoi jouse vutvam asoh gam tan, vanchung sanga kon'in selhah in a um’e. Pakai a lunghan behseh jeh in aHou-In jeng jong khoto na anei tapoi.
\v 2 Khotona beihel in Pakaiyin Isreal insung jouse a subeiyin, a lunghan nan Jerusalem kulpi len jouse a suchip gam’e. Aman alenggam ule alengteu jong jum tah in tol jep nan anei gam tai.
\v 3 Pakai lunghan na noi a Isreal thaneina jouse a mangthah gam tai. Galmi ten ahin delkhum nauva jong a huhdoh tapon ahi. Aman Isreal gam pumpi chu meikong in ahal lhah banginahal gam tan ahi.
\v 4 Aman agalmite bangin amite chung a athalpi kaosan akoiyin, agollhang hoilai jouse thagam dingin atha aje doh in ahi. Loupitah Jerusalem chunga alunghan na meikong bangin abunglhan ahi.
\v 5 Pakaiyin Isrealte hi agalmi bangina suhchip in, Aman loupitah Jerusalem chunga lungkhamna le mitlhilon angahna beijin alhun khum sah’e.
\v 6 Aman Hou-In jong honsunga buh kisa bangina sulhun, Pakaiyin anikho thengho ahin, cholngah nikhoho le kut nikho thengho ahin suhmil thei leuvin asubei jin leng ho leh thempu ho jong a lungsat na noija a subei gam tan ahi.
\v 7 Pakaiyin amaicham jeng jong a nuse in, amuntheng jeng jong nahsah louvin akoiyin, Jerusalem lengpa inpi ho jong galmiho a pedoh’e. Ama hon Pakai Hou-In sung chu golnop kibolni bangin, o’thongje jun apoh chei choi jengun ahi.
\v 8 Khopi hoitah Jerusalem chu apal jouse suhlhah ding angaiton, aman atoh gon bang bangina sulhu soh tan ahi. Hijeh chun pal ho leh palvum jouse jong amasanga alhusoh tan ahi.
\v 9 Jerusalem kelkot phung jouse jong tol ah aki jamchap soh helin, akel kot gol jouse jong aheh bongin a sumang soh tai. Jerusalem lengpa leh milen milal ho jong namtin vaipi lah a akithe thangsoh taove. Danthu kitila abeitan Themgao hon jong Pakaiya kon'in mu anei tapouve.
\v 10 Khopi hoitah Jerusalem sunga lamkaiho tolla thip beh chan atouvun, a lujang uva leivui a kinuvin, khaodip pon akisil un, Jerusalem nungah jousen jum le jachat tothon a kaiku jeng taove.
\v 11 Kamitlhi twi kan tokahin ka kap jingin, ka lungsung achip lhatai. Kholai dunga chapang neocha ho athileh aki saisaijuva, kamite hahsatna khankho ka mu jeh in ka lungthim sung jong akap doh jengin ahi.
\v 12 Anuteu henga, neh ding le donding kangaichai tin athumun. Galsatpa galmunna akimavo bangin, kholai dunga thabeiyin apengun, anu teuvin apom nau chunga ahinkho’u abeithu thu jengin ahi.
\v 13 Hichan geija lungkhamna toh ho chunga ipi kasei thei ding ham? Vo Jerusalem Chanute, na lung hesoh naohi ipitoh kitekah ding ahm? Oh Zion chanu thengte iti ka lhamon jou ding nahiuvem? Ajeh chu na thohgim nao hi twikhanglen bangin athuh jengin koiham na boldam jou diu vah?
\v 14 Na themgao teuvinla jouthu ngen leh ngol-hoi thu ngen na seipeh uvin, na soh chan nauva konna nahung kiledoh theina diuva na chonsetnau phondoh peh ding la ago pouvin, chutia bolsang'in jouthu ngen jeng apat thu uvin, thil dihlou ngen na kinep sah jiuvin ahi.
\v 15 Ache le avahle ho jousen na nel peh un khopi hoitah Jerusalem hi noise tah in atot chatvai khummun; “hiche hi vannoi leisetna khopi hoipen vannoi pumpin achoi sang uchu ham?” atiuve.
\v 16 Nagalmite jousen na nelpeh un noise tah in anop nop na seikhumun, “suhmang dinga phat sottah ina nga’u chu tun ahung guilhung tai!” atiuve.
\v 17 Ahinlah hiche hi Pakaiyin a tohgon chu aboldoh ahin, hamsetna hunglhung dinga ana gonsa chu a suh bulhit ahi. Aman Jerusalem chu khotona beihella ana suhbei ahin, Aman agalmiteu chu amaho chunga thaneina anapeh ahi.
\v 18 Khopi hoi Jerusalem, Pakai angah hakan kap in, Sun le jan in vadung bangin na mitlhi long hen. kicholdo hihhel in; Na mitlhi lon jong tansah dan.
\v 19 Janlai jongleh thouvin pengjah jengin. Pakai angah na lung ngaichat twi bangin lonsah in. Nachateu dingin na taonao khut chu domsang jingun, ajeh chu kholai dung jousea gilkela lhalhop gamsoh ahitaove.
\v 20 Vo Pakai hiche thoh gimna hi gel temin!
\p Na chate hi hiti lom lom’a nabol jing ding hitam? Minuten a angsunga hung kitolchem, achateu kisanhi aneh jeng diu hitam?
\p Thempu ho leh themgao ho kisan hi Pakai Hou-In sunga kithat jeng ding hitam?
\p 
\v 21 Ven, lamlen dunga kijam chap ho khu –
\p Khangdong le tehseho, Numei chapang ho leh pasal chapang ho, Galmite chemjam a thijeng ahiuve. Na lung han petin nathat gamin, Lungsetna beihelin nabol’e.
\p 
\v 22 Golvah nikhoa mipi nakou khom bangin,
\p Muntin jousea tijatna nakoukhom’e.
\p Pakai lunghanna nikhon, Koi macha a sohcha le ahingdoh a um poi. Kahin khoukhah le kahin puihoi chate chengse, Galmiten a thatgamsoh heltai.
\c 3
\s1 Themgao Lunghemna Leh Kinepna
\p 
\v 1 Pakai lunghanna tanggolla kon hungpotdoh thohgimna chu keima tah in kamuchet ahi.
\v 2 Aman vah jouse daltanin,
\p Muthim lah a eipuilut e.
\p 
\v 3 Nilhum keijin avel vellin keima dounan ka chunga a khut a lamin ahi.
\v 4 Aman kaphe leh kavun agotsah jenge. Kagu kachang jong a sungoi jengin ahi.
\v 5 Aman lunggimna leh gentheina eisun khumin chatmo hellin eilha tai.
\v 6 Aman mithisa ho bangin,
\p Muthim lah a eivuiye.
\p 
\v 7 Aman pal eikai khumin,
\p Keima ka jamdoh thei tapoi.
\p Thihkhao gihtah in jong eikan chah e.
\p 
\v 8 Keima kapengjah jeng vang'in,
\p Aman ka taona adalten del tai.
\p 
\v 9 Songpal sangtah in ka lampi akhah tannin;
\p Ka lampi eisuh setpeh e.
\p 
\v 10 Keima man dingin,
\p Kei le vompi banginkiselin eichang lei.
\p 
\v 11 Aman ka lampia kon'in eimanin eimal tel tel in,
\p Hesoh genthei le panpi beiyin eilhai.
\p 
\v 12 Aman athal-pou aloisalin,
\p Keima abidoiyin eineiye.
\p 
\v 13 Ka lungchang laitah a,
\p Athalchang chu a kaplut jenge.
\p 
\v 14 Kamiten nuisatbepseu kahitai.
\p Nilhum keijin musetna la eisah khum uve.
\p 
\v 15 Aman lunggimna jengin eisu dimin, Lungkhamna khacheh khon chu eidon sah e.
\v 16 Aman songchang eilhai sahin, vutvai lah a eilehluttan ahi.
\v 17 Chamna chu eilah mang pehin,
\p Phatthei channa ding chu keidin gelphah ahi tapoi.
\p 
\v 18 Ka loupina nikho akichai tan,
\p Pakaiya ka kinepna jouse jong ahomkiu ahitai, tin kakap jah jeng tai.
\p 
\v 19 Kathoh gimna leh ka lengvaina hinkho hin eisugim thei val jeng e.
\v 20 Ka thohgimna le in le kagentheina hi, seiya seijou hoi ahita poi.
\v 21 Ahin hiche hi kahin geldoh teng,
\p Kinepna kanei jou jin ahi:
\p 
\v 22 Pakai nei ngailutna dihtah chun beitih anei pon,
\p Amikhotona jong atangdeh poi.
\p 
\v 23 A kitahna hi longlou ahin,
\p Ami khotona jong jingkah sehin athah jingin ahi.
\p 
\v 24 Kahinna ka lhagaovin aseijin Pakai hi keima gou ahi. Hijeh chun Ama a kakinepna hi um jing ahije.
\v 25 Pakai ging jingte leh hinna dinga hol jing tedinga phatah ahi.
\v 26 Hijeh chun Pakaiya konna huhhing na mun'a dinga thipbeh cha nga hat angaije.
\v 27 Chu leh khan don laiya Ama angsunga kipehlut leh Ami thununna koljon kikhum lut aphai.
\v 28 Ama chu Pakaiyin atohsah nomna dungjuijin thipbeh in aching seh in ngah jing hen.
\v 29 Amaho chun amaijun tollam ngatnu henlang kijammu hen ajeh chu ama hon ajona leh akinepna’u dungjuiya amu thei diu ahi.
\v 30 Amaho chun a ngei phe bengho chu alangkhat jong dopeh uhenlang agalmi ten anoise nau jong kisan uhen.
\v 31 Ajeh chu koimacha hi Pakaiyin apaidoh paipai aumpoi.
\v 32 Aman lungkhamna asosahje vang'in ami khotona dimset jeh chun angailutna ahop jinge.
\v 33 Ajeh chu Pakai hi milungkham sahle alungthim sunhat peh ahi along lhaina ahipoi.
\v 34 Mihon gamsunga songkullut ho chu akelngoi tol chotpha jongleh’u,
\v 35 Hitobang miho chun Pathen douna in midang chan ding dolho lahpeh jonglehu,
\v 36 Chuleh aman a thutan nauva achan ding dol’u thudih chu chansah hih jong leu, hitiho jouse Pakaiyin amu sohkei hilou ham?
\v 37 Pakai phatsah louva koiham thilho hung soh doh na ding thupeh neithei ding chu?
\v 38 Chungnungpen Pathen'in thilpha le thilse ahin sosah ji hilou ham?
\v 39 Chuti ahileh mihon eiho e-chonset jeh uva engbolna e-chan jiuhi i-kiphin thei ding uham?
\v 40 Chuti louvin, eihon e-chonna u hi kikhuol’u hitin chuleh Pakai kom’a iki lehei kit lou diu ham?
\v 41 Eihon e-lung thim ule e-khut’u Van Pathen anga domsangu hitin seiju hite,
\v 42 Keiho nangma dounan ka chonse tauvin nangman nei ngaidam pouvin ahi,
\v 43 Nangman na lunghanna neibuh lhah khum tauvin chuleh khotona beihelin neidel khumun nei that gam tauve.
\v 44 Mei lah a na kiselin, katao na’u na kom'ahunglhung jou tapoi,
\v 45 Nangman chitin namtin lah a thet le notthapin nei koitauvin ahi.
\v 46 “Ka melmateuvin
\p Keiho dounan thu asei sei jingun.
\p 
\v 47 Keiho kichat le tijatnan
\p Ka dimset tauve,
\p Ajeh chu keiho kimana, kisugepa amang thah kahi tauve.”
\p 
\v 48 Ka miteu kisuhmang jeh'in,
\p Ka mitlhi’u twilon in along e!
\p 
\v 49 Kamitlhiu tanglouhel in alonge;
\p Tang louding ahi,
\p 
\v 50 Pakaiyin Van'a konna ahin vetsuh,
\p Ahin lainatpi tokah un,
\p 
\v 51 Jerusalem Chanute khankho gelnan,
\p Ka lungthim hi apohkeh ding akisa jing’e.
\p 
\v 52 Keiman kasuhset louhel galmin,
\p Vaacha bangin eideljam e.
\p 
\v 53 Kokhuh’a ei nolutun,
\p Ka chunga song eiset khume.
\p 
\v 54 Ka luchang geiyin twiyin eichupin, “Athi ding kahitai” tin ka peng jah’e.
\v 55 Ahin kokhuh sunga kon'in, Pakai,
\p Nangma kahin kouve.
\p 
\v 56 Nangman ka kouna najan, “Kataona nei sanpehin,
\p Panpi ngehna a kataona nei san peh e!”
\p 
\v 57 Keiman kahin kou chun nangma na hungin “kicha hih in” neiti.
\v 58 Pakai nangman ka thutanpa nahin, ka chung thu nei seipehin!
\p Ajeh chu eihuhduha Nang na hi.
\p 
\v 59 Pakai ama hon ka chunga i-chan geija thilse abol’u hitam namu sohkeiye,
\p kathu nei kholtohpihin lang, kadihna neitahlang pehin,
\p 
\v 60 Ka galmiten kei douna tohgon aneiyu
\p Nangman nahesohkeiye.
\p 
\v 61 Pakai nangin eitaitomnao na jasohkeijin chuleh ka chunga thilse abolgot hou jong na hesohkeiye.
\v 62 Ka galmite ka chunga akihou un
\p Keima dounan akihou lhi jingun ahi.
\p 
\v 63 Amaho khu ven! Atoupetu hihen adinpetu hijongleh, keima nuisatna la jeng asaove.
\v 64 Pakai ka chunga thilse abol jouseu hi, Amaho chunga chuhsahin.
\v 65 Amaho hi lungtahna leh sei ngailouna lungthim penlang,
\p Achunguva sapsetna chuh sah in.
\p 
\v 66 Achung uvah na lunghanna chuhsah inlang,
\p Pakai vansem ho noi jahin amaho khu suhmang tan.
\c 4
\s1 Zion Kisuh Nenna
\p 
\v 1 Sana jong adeite khuta among joutai!
\p Sana hoi pen jong amoljeng tai.
\p Muntheng sunga um songmantam ho jeng, jong lam lhongp dunga athangsoh tai.
\p 
\v 2 Veuvin Jerusalem chate,
\p Mipha chomtah tahsan hoitah tah sanga mantam jo ho chu,
\p Tun leibelho tobangin abol tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 3 Sialte jengin jong anoute avah jiuvin, ahinla kami Isrealten avah pouvin ahi. Neldi gam'a vacha len “Vagonsang” hon achasenteu anahsah lou bangun ama hon jong a nahsah pouvin ahi.
\v 4 Dangchahin achateu lhei jouse adanga abehden jouve. Achateu gilkelin an aholun,
\p Ahin koiman pehding aneipoi.
\p 
\v 5 An twitah tah ana neji ho chun tun lampi dunga khut don apang tauvin ahi. Phatkhatna vonhoi tahtah anavon ho chun tun thilnen kikholna munhoa neh ding aholun ahi.
\v 6 Kamite chonsetna hi Sodom mite chonsetna sangin alenjon ahi. \x + \xo 4:6 \xt Semtilbu 19:24\x*
\p Hiche munna chun hetman louvin suhmangna nasatah anachun koimacha akithopi thei ana umpoiye.
\p 
\v 7 Ka lengteu jong phat khat chun amel-hoidanu chu bongnoi leh buhbang sangin ana bangjon, amai’u jong songmantam bangin ana vah'in ahi.
\v 8 Tunvang amelu jong meihol sangin avomjoi.
\p Lampi dunga jong koiman ahedoh thei tapouve.
\p Avunu jong agu uva abehdan gamin, thing go bangin, agon atah jenge.
\p 
\v 9 Chamjamma kithat ho chu gelkella thiho sangin avangphajo ahitaove.
\p Ajeh chu lou laiya neh aput tahlou jeh'in keltho hin amangthah jitaove.
\p 
\v 10 Masanga mi lainatpi theitah tah nute hon achateu chu neh dingin akihon gam tauve. Ama hon gim hesoha konna hoi dohna dingin achateu chu ana nejengun ahi. \x + \xo 4:10 \xt Danbu Ni Na 28:57; Ezekiel 5:10\x*
\v 11 Tunvang alunghanna a kon chun Pakai alungna chim tai. Alunghanna hoise tah chu abuhlhah ahitai. Jerusalem'a lunghanna mei ana koudohin hichun khopi chu aleibul kiphuna gei chun ana hallha jeng’e.
\v 12 Leist lengte ahin - Vannoi mite koiman -
\p Jerusalem kelkot sunga galmi alutthei ding chu ana tahsan pouve.
\p 
\v 13 Ahinlah a themgao ho chonsetna leh a thempu ho chonsetna jeh chun hiti hin anasohdoh tan ahi.
\p Amaho chonset jeh a themmona bei miho thisan kisoa, khopi kisuboh ahi.
\p 
\v 14 Amaho hi lamlhongpi dunga ana vahle uvin mi thisana akisubohun koiman amaho atongkha ngam pouvin ahi.
\v 15 Mipiten chemangun tin asamun aboh nahi tauve, neitong khahihun atiuve. Amaho gamla tah in ajamun gamchom mite lah a avahle uvin ahinlah koiman achensah nom pouvin ahi.
\v 16 Pakai ama tah in amaho hi apanpi nom tapouvin muchom chomma athethang gam’u ahitai. Mipihon jong thempuho hi anahsah tapouvin, alamkai hou jong jana anei tapouvin ahi.
\v 17 Eihon i-pankhompi houvin eihung huhdoh diuvin ingaichauvin, eikithopi theiloudiu nam mite kom jenga jong panpi ingaichauvin a phachom pon ahi.
\v 18 Thi ding kichat jeh'in lampi dunga jong kavahle ngam pouvin, amahthah ding nikhou jong ahung naitan, amah thah ding ihitauve.
\v 19 Igalmiteu hi mulaopi sangin jong aleng hat jon,
\p Molsang chung dunga jammang go jong leuhen eimudohdiu ahin, gamthip langa kisel jong leuhen hiche munna jong chu eina chan nahlai dingu ahiye.
\p 
\v 20 Eihon leiset nam pumpi jouse hoa konna eihuhdoh diuva ina monpiu Pakai thaonu i-engpau jeng jong, akiselna munna kon'in a mandoh tauvin ahi.
\v 21 Vo! Edom mite Uz gamsunga hi nakipa theiju hinam? Ahin nangin jong Pakai lunghanna khkonna konna hi na don tei ding ahi. Nang jeng jong na jukhamna munna sagoh keova naki koi ding ahi.
\v 22 Vo khopi hoitah Jerusalem, naki engbolna nihko kichai ding ahitai,
\p Naki engbolna gam'a konna nahung kile vah ding ahitai.
\p Ahinlah Edom naki engbolna hi kipan bepseu ahinalaiye;
\p Na chonsetna ho jouse hung kiphongdoh vah ding ahitai.
\c 5
\s1 Kiledohna Dinga Taona
\p 
\v 1 Pakai ka chunguva thilsoh ho hi hingeldoh temin, ven ichan geija vetset ka chan’u hitam?
\v 2 Ka goulo diu chengse hi namchom miho achang tauvin,
\p Ka in ka lou jouseu la gamchom miho’a ahitai.
\p 
\v 3 Keiho hi nunei lou panei lou kahi tauvin, kanuteu jong meithai ahi gam tauve.
\v 4 Ka dondiu twi jeng jong kakichoh thu diuvin aumdoh tan,
\p Ti ding thing jeng jong kakichoh thudiu ahitai.
\p 
\v 5 Eihin nungdelteuvin eihin phah pai dingu ahitan,
\p Keiho ka haisam tauvin, ahinlah kingahna ding mun ka neipouve.
\p 
\v 6 Neh leh chah ning lhinga kanei jouseu, Ka kihinso jou nadiuvin Egypt leh Asssyria khutna ka kipelut tauvin ahi.
\v 7 Kapu kapateu ana chonseuvin ahinlah amaho athi gam tauve,
\p Hijeh chun amaho chan ding thoh gimna leh engbolna hi keiho chunga achu tan ahi.
\p 
\v 8 Ka sohteu chu tun keiho Pakaiyin apang gamtauvin, ahinlah koima eihuhdoh diu aum pon ahi.
\v 9 Gamsun’a pum hatin vai ahop jeh'in thi ding kicha pum pumin anneh kakiholun ahi.
\v 10 Kel khoh jeh'in ka vousou tapkonga changlhah kikang bangin avom gam tai.
\v 11 Kagal miteuvin Jerusalem'a numei ho Judah khosunga nungah khangdong ho kichep nan anei gam tauve.
\v 12 Ka lengteu jong akhutpiuvin akhaisangun,
\p Ka lamkaiteu jong noise tah in ei bolpeh tauvin ahi.
\p 
\v 13 Gollhang ho chu sumhei goi dingin akaimangun, chuleh pasal chapang ho chu tiding thing aputsahnauva a lonlele jeng tauvin ahi.
\v 14 Lamkai ho khopi kelkot ngahin apang tapouve. Khangthahten lam leh la sah abol tapouvin ahi.
\v 15 Kana lam nao chu lung khamna asohdoh tan,
\p Ka lungsung uva kipana abeitai.
\p 
\v 16 Ka luchang uva kon'in ka lallukhuhu alhamang gam tai. Ka chonset jeh un ka chung uva sapsetna achu tai.
\v 17 Hijeh hin kalungu alhalhop tan chuleh kamit uvah mitlhi adimtan ahi.
\v 18 Ajeh chu Jerusalem hi akeosehin aki jam tan, Sialten lhat nan anei tauve.
\v 19 Ahinlah Pakai nangma abang na hi jing jeng e, nalal touna chu akhang khangin aum jing e.
\v 20 Ipi dinga nei suhmil jing nahlaiyu ham? Ipi dinga donlou dai louva neikoi nahlaiyu ham?
\v 21 O Pakai neikiledohsah kitnun lang nangma kom'a nei puilut kittauvin! Ka kipanao masa chu neipe kittauvin!
\v 22 Ahilou leh neipui doh mong mong diu hitam? Ole Ka chunguva nalunghangjing nalai ham? 
